Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.17,0:00:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,MUNICH\N(GERMANY)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.92,0:00:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Domo. We look forward to working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Domo. We look forward to it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, why don't we play\Na round of golf together?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.10,0:00:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, but please go easy on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.19,0:00:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We look forward to doing\Nmore business with you in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.94,0:00:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Domo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.48,0:00:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Domo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.69,0:00:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Domo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"Domo" this, "domo" that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.62,0:00:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All that stuff makes no sense at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, domo, domo! Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Our meeting went on longer than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.83,0:00:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Iwai, from Kadofuku Corporation's\NMunich office.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.67,0:00:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Inspector Lunge of the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.68,0:00:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.14,0:00:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Domo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.85,0:00:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"Domo" and a bow?\NWell, I wasn't expecting that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.98,0:01:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A coffee, please. And give him a refill.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector,\Nyou asked to speak with Yamamoto,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but he's in the Czech Republic\Nfor business right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.66,0:01:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He should be back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.29,0:01:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He sounds like a busy man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.29,0:01:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.41,0:01:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that the mogul Mr. Schuwald
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.46,0:01:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,has come out of seclusion\Nand has gotten involved in business again,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.92,0:01:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,all his subsidiaries
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.96,0:01:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and their related businesses\Naround Germany have been extremely active.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.43,0:01:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us Japanese businessmen\Nare busy vying for his attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.43,0:01:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's he laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.39,0:01:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that Yamamoto\Ncan't meet with you today,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm just about as familiar\Nwith Kenzo Tenma as he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.99,0:01:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.95,0:01:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised to hear\Nthat you're still investigating him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.16,0:01:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The case still hasn't been solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was shocked when I heard\Nthat Mr. Tenma was a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"Shocked?" Was it really so unbelievable?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"Unbelievable" isn't a strong enough word.\NThere's no way he's a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, to be perfectly honest,\Nhe could never do anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Three years ago, I went out\Ndrinking with him a couple of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's not a bad person,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,does that make him a good person?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.95,0:02:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A good person?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.91,0:02:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he was more of a reserved person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.41,0:02:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is a reserved person a good person?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, what I mean is\Nhe wasn't an unfriendly guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.48,0:04:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Japanese people don't\Nordinarily wear this kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Japanese are skillful with chopsticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Japanese. Domo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I am…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:04:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh… Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.47,0:04:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:04:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.51,0:05:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I called because I heard you're in Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I live here in Munich now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,, Dad, my child's been born.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right? Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot has happened between us,\Nbut I want you to see your grandchild.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you come see us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. Can we meet tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. After 6:00 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll meet in Marienplatz.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye. Domo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.85,0:05:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.23,0:05:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,TACHIBANA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.\NYou're pretty good with those chopsticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:05:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, there are a lot of foreigners
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,who use chopsticks better\Nthan many Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, Dr. Takahashi,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,as Tenma's former co-worker,\Nwhat was your impression of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My impression? Well, let's see…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We got along pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He can be indecisive at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"Yet?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When he had a scalpel in his hand,\Nhe was a different man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.64,0:06:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He was called a genius neurosurgeon,\Nbut it certainly wasn't an exaggeration.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What about his parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't like talking about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He said his father\Nand older brother were doctors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt he had a choice\Nabout becoming a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, he told me\Nthat after becoming a doctor in Germany,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.04,0:06:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,he hadn't been back to Japan even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.88,0:07:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, his parents didn't even come\Nto Germany when the scandal broke,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and didn't even do anything\Nto prove their son's innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.97,0:07:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you could say\Nthey weren't a tight-knit family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,KADOFUKU CORPORATION
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamamoto just called to let us know\Nhe's arriving in Munich from Prague,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but he said he has to go visit a client\Nbefore returning here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He sounds like a busy man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he'd drop by the pub\Nwe're heading off to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"Pub?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you join us too,\NInspector Lunge?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.39,0:07:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This could be a good opportunity.\NYou can always use new contacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, tonight I've got…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you could say\Nthey weren't a tight-knit family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I am…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice idea. I'd be glad to join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.27,0:08:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,KARAOKE PUB OEDO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Iwai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.29,0:08:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a song, Inspector Lunge?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:08:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's my song. Let's sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.22,0:09:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's hear it!\N-All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.23,0:09:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-Nice! Keep it up!\N-Way to go! Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.03,0:09:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not fit into Japanese society.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't ask for help now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no place to call home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I am…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there. Domo, domo. Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:10:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, you're here, Yamamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.65,0:10:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Inspector Lunge\Nwho I mentioned on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, domo. I'm Yamamoto of\Nthe Munich office of Kadofuku Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.78,0:10:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Domo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How did the meeting\Nwith Mr. Kocht in the Czech Republic go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.87,0:10:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a really tough customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that reminds me. I found that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.25,0:10:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing Schuwald's secretary,\Nthat young blonde guy, wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Did you find that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, getting on\Nhis secretary's good side
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is the best way\Nto get business done with Schuwald.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to a bunch of used book shops\Nin Prague before I finally found a copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.65,0:10:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is that picture book?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in pretty bad shape\Nand the cover is gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but if we wrap it up nicely,\Nit will still impress him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.74,0:10:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. Beer, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.83,0:10:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, go right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in Czech.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is my song!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.34,0:11:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-Okay! Let's hear it!\N-All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.34,0:11:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now for the real pro, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.68,0:11:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,MUNICH POLICE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.23,0:11:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector, what do you have\Nthat dictionary out for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm translating Czech.\N-Czech?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.32,0:11:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it related to the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it has nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd investigate\Nanything not related to a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.62,0:11:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to know what the text meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The inspector looking at a picture book?\NNever expected that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.47,0:11:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"Look at me."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.43,0:12:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"The monster inside me has
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,grown so large," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So Johan has finally\Nstarted manipulating that bigwig.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Gillen,\Nyou told me before about this Johan guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell\Nthat Johan is a complete monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I've killed a lot of people myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but he's become the kind of person\Nthat I wanted to become.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.67,0:12:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan's my hero now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. There's something else\Nthat I'd like to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were Johan, what would you do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd murder his parents, the Lieberts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:12:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Liebert!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.45,0:13:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Liebert!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see? I got bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Liebert!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.51,0:13:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a psychologist?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but what is it\Nyou want with us, Dr. Reichwein?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't waste your time\Nwith a long explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come to you about\Nyour adopted son, Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan? "Adopted?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NThat boy is our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use playing dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The grave of your true son is in Bruntal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You took advantage of\Nthe town records being destroyed in a fire
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and applied for a new birth certificate\Nto make it look like your child is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:13:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you implying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.84,0:14:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't come here to threaten you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here for your own sakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.68,0:14:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.35,0:14:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a report about Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.69,0:14:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,About Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It was compiled by a certain man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.03,0:14:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This man once visited\Nto sell us insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Richard Braun,\Na former police detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A former police detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dead now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The story begins in 1986
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,when a certain East German\Ngovernment official defected to the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he after money?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.31,0:14:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Money? No, he's not interested in money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why has he curried favor\Nwith a billionaire?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:15:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-Didn't you play that game as a kid?\N-What game?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.69,0:15:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd find a line of ants…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'd mess up their line\Nand screw with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My god…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot possibly believe\Nsuch a frightening story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is ludicrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.43,0:15:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand why\Nyou don't want to believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.14,0:15:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost your child when he was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You were never able to have more children.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.23,0:15:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But then a young man showed up\Nwho was around
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the same age as your son,\Nand he had money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave you this magnificent house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave you this beautiful garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And he gave you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.99,0:15:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I perfectly understand\Nwhy you believe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:15:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,However,\Nthe things in this report are the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.63,0:16:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me who the heck he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan is a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.31,0:16:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan is a kind boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.98,0:16:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He's smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.69,0:16:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a clever boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.44,0:16:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He's our reason for living.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.74,0:16:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been playing his parents\Nfor five years,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but is that all you can say about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You know absolutely nothing about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.96,0:16:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you. I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.84,0:16:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan killed my friend Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And right now, a man named Dr. Tenma is…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,about to do the unthinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:17:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you will end up like\Nthe middle-aged couples in this report.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.44,0:17:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They were all foster parents\Nwho raised Johan. And they were…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,all murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, leave this place with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.27,0:17:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The apple tree has sprouted\Nsome small fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Next year, they'll be even bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hardly wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I can hardly wait too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:18:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan told the children that\Nhe's about to be killed by a Japanese man?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. What do you think about what he said?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,To be frank,\Nthat guy doesn't have a death wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.01,0:18:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.26,0:18:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure. It's hard to know\Nwhat a hero is thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can tell you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If the world ended in a nuclear war,\Nhe would survive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he means\Nthere's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I will admit, everything we've done\Nso far has been in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't even save Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.76,0:18:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Reichwein…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't even been able\Nto track down Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.39,0:19:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't even stop him trying\Nto kill Johan. It's all been in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Reichwein, we need\Nto stay calm and think this over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.11,0:19:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mess with a line of ants, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Even ants have souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.54,0:19:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point, we must risk everything\Nand bring the fight to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll meet with that mogul Schuwald\Nand tell him everything we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Do they want 50 more chairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.52,0:19:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang, they are really packing them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this for Mr. Schuwald's\Nbook donation ceremony tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.28,0:19:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Important people are coming out\Nof the woodwork to attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:20:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nowadays, anytime Mr. Schuwald\Nmakes a move, it's a huge deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The library is about to close.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.05,0:20:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The library is about to close.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but could you get that book for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.58,0:20:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that Czech dictionary.\NI can't reach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:20:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure. This?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.14,0:21:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thank you, I appreciate it.\N-No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I borrowed a Czech picture book,\Nbut I can't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.44,0:21:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.65,0:21:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend of mine suddenly fainted\Nwhen he read this picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought whatever is in this book\Nmight have had something to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.49,0:21:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your friend all right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He's just fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.72,0:21:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see here…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.05,0:21:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"Once upon a time, in a land far away,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.31,0:21:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,there lived a nameless monster."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.77,0:22:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"The monster was dying to have a name."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.62,0:22:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"So he decided to set out on a journey."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.87,0:22:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What a strange book.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.96,0:22:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We're closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.46,0:22:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.42,0:22:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're closed tomorrow\Nbecause of the ceremony.
